releases.name: v1.0.8
releases.body:
Most probably the latest version.  
I don't use it anymore, and there is an official UI in the way anyway.

releases.name: v1.0.7
releases.body:
Improvements:
- Better look
- Evolve pokemon through the UI
- Display snipes on the map
- Bug fixes

releases.name: v1.0.6
releases.body:
New features:
- New installer for 32 bits
- Transfer Pokemon (new bot version from the source)
- Fix follow player
- Fix auto update

Contains:
- 64 bits installer version (default)
- 32 bits installer version
- Zip for 64 bits
- Zip for 32 bits
  Should work on Mac & Linux using "npm install && npm start" from the source.

releases.name: v1.0.5
releases.body:
Incubator should display correctly
Popup can be deactivated on settings
Item and Pokemon available in English, French and German
Bug fixes.

As always, latest version of NecroBot or MobBot are needed.

releases.name: v1.0.4
releases.body:
Inventory
Should display catches correctly
Clear map button (to easily change bot)

releases.name: v1.0.3
releases.body:
Alternativre map (choose in top right)
Can see your pokemon (lower right)
Can see your eggs (lower right)
Toast when new pokemon catch
Better handling of snipe (not on map, only toast)

v0.4.0 of the bot is probably needed for everything to work.

releases.name: v1.0.2
releases.body:
Add German locale for pokemon names
Display Pokestop
Can display pokemon list
Nicer icons

the bot needs to be up to date
